### Reports — daily aggregates via pandas
###
### Backed by GET /api/reports/daily. Date range optional; defaults to today (UTC).
### Used by n8n's "02 — Daily Anomaly Report" workflow on a cron and by the
### dashboard Home view.

@host = http://localhost:8000

# @name login
POST {{host}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=admin&password=admin123


# ============================================================================
# GET /api/reports/daily
# ============================================================================
### Today (no params)
GET {{host}}/api/reports/daily
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}

###

### Specific day (single date — fromDate == toDate)
GET {{host}}/api/reports/daily?from_date=2026-04-24&to_date=2026-04-25
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}

###

### Date range (last 7 days)
GET {{host}}/api/reports/daily?from_date=2026-04-19&to_date=2026-04-25
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}

###

### Empty range (deep past) → totalOrders=0, all collections empty
GET {{host}}/api/reports/daily?from_date=1970-01-01&to_date=1970-01-01
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
